night. can she?

773
00:36:42.839 --> 00:36:44.908
I was crying for hours.

774
00:36:44.933 --> 00:36:47.903
We did... write it.

775
00:36:47.945 --> 00:36:49.247
I turned it in this morning.

776
00:36:49.272 --> 00:36:50.941
