957
00:47:25.244 --> 00:47:27.413
(MYSTERIOUS MUSIC PLAYING)

958
00:47:33.323 --> 00:47:34.625
(LIGHT BUZZING)

959
00:47:35.670 --> 00:47:38.106
(RAT SCREECHING)

960
00:47:39.574 --> 00:47:43.210
